Julie Bishop (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Julie_Bishop_(actress) 0 Julie Bishop (born Jacqueline Brown, August 30, 1914 – August 30, 2001) was an American film and television actress. She appeared in more than 80 films between 1923 and 1957, billed in some as Jacqueline Wells.
